<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #1f4632; padding: 2rem;">
  <h1 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Payment received! 🎉</h1>
  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
    Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
    Thank you for your payment! Your <%= @subscription.plan %> subscription is now <strong>active</strong>. ♻️
  </p>

  <% if @is_new %>
    <%# ---- NEW CUSTOMER ---- %>
    <% if @subscription.Commercial? %>
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
        <strong>Your subscription details:</strong><br>
        Duration: <%= @subscription.duration %> months<br>
        Buckets per collection: <%= @subscription.buckets_per_collection %> × <%= @subscription.bucket_size %>L buckets<br>
        Collection day: <%= @subscription.collection_day %>
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
        Alfred will deliver your commercial buckets in the week of <strong><%= @subscription.start_date.strftime('%A, %-d %B') %></strong>.
        Once you have organic waste ready, leave the full buckets out before 8am on your collection day.
      </p>
    <% else %>
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
        <strong>Your subscription details:</strong><br>
        Plan: <%= @subscription.plan %><br>
        Duration: <%= @subscription.duration %> months<br>
        Collection day: <%= @subscription.collection_day %>
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
        Alfred will deliver your starter kit in the week of <strong><%= @subscription.start_date.strftime('%A, %-d %B') %></strong>.
        Your kit includes a compost bin, compostable bags, and a guide to get you going.
      </p>
    <% end %>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
      <strong>What happens next?</strong><br>
      • Alfred will collect from your address every <%= @subscription.collection_day %><br>
      • Please leave your compost out before 8am on collection day<br>
      • You can manage your subscription anytime at <%= link_to 'gooi.me', root_url, style: "color: #FBB718; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;" %>
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
      Thanks for joining the food waste revolution! 🌱
    </p>

  <% else %>
    <%# ---- RETURNING CUSTOMER ---- %>
    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
      Welcome back! Your <%= @subscription.plan %> subscription is active and your collections will continue every <strong><%= @subscription.collection_day %></strong> as usual.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
      You can manage your subscription anytime at <%= link_to 'gooi.me', root_url, style: "color: #FBB718; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;" %>.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
      Thanks for gooiing again! 🌱
    </p>

  <% end %>

  <p style="margin: 2rem 0;">
    <a href="<%= manage_url %>"
       style="background-color: #FBB718; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 40px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">
      View My Account
    </a>
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">Kristen</p>
  <%= image_tag image_url('email-signature.png'), alt: "Kristen Kennedy email signature", style: "max-width: 250px; margin-top: 10px;" %>
</div>
